OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FIran has reportedly sent the US a
OL,7,Ffresh proposal for ending the war, as
OL,8,Fthe Trump administration faces its 60-
OL,9,Fday deadline for congressional
OL,10,Fapproval.
OL,12,FThe proposal is being shared with the
OL,13,FUS via Pakistani mediators, Iranian
OL,14,Fstate media agency IRNA reported on
OL,15,FFriday.
OL,17,FAs he left the White House for Florida
OL,18,Fon Friday, US President Donald Trump
OL,19,Fsaid he was not satisfied with the
OL,20,Flatest proposal but that the US was
OL,21,Fnegotiating with Iran by phone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
