OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777759863
OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FHe told reporters that Iran "wants to
OL,7,Fmake a deal".
OL,9,FThe two nations have been locked in a
OL,10,Fstandoff for nearly four weeks after a
OL,11,Fceasefire was agreed on April 7.
OL,13,FThe US has been engaged in a naval
OL,14,Fblockade of Iranian ports along the
OL,15,FStrait of Hormuz since April 13, in
OL,16,Fresponse to Iran almost entirely
OL,17,Fclosing the waterway to the rest of
OL,18,Fthe world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
