OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOil prices are currently around $111
OL,12,F(about #81.41) a barrel for Brent
OL,13,FCrude, the global benchmark.
OL,15,FThe Trump administration recently
OL,16,Fclaimed the war was effectively over
OL,17,Fas it hit a legal deadline for
OL,18,Fcongressional approval.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
