OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FUnder the War Powers Resolution of
OL,7,F1973, the US president must end a
OL,8,Fmilitary campaign after 60 days,
OL,9,Funless Congress declares war or
OL,10,Fauthorises the use of military force,
OL,11,For a 30-day extension is requested.
OL,13,FTrump formally notified lawmakers of
OL,14,Fthe war on March 2, which would mean
OL,15,Fthe 60-day period ends on May 1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
