PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777759863
OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FHowever a senior administration
OL,7,Fofficial, who spoke to AP on the
OL,8,Fcondition of anonymity, said the war
OL,9,Fhad since been "terminated", as
OL,10,Fneither the US and Iran had exchanged
OL,11,Ffire since April 7.
OL,13,F"For war powers resolution purposes,
OL,14,Fthe hostilities that began on
OL,15,FSaturday, February 28, have
OL,16,Fterminated," they said.
OL,26,@xD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
