OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FUS Defence Secretary Pete Hegseth also
OL,7,Fsaid during a hearing on Thursday that
OL,8,Fthe Trump administration's
OL,9,Funderstanding is that the "60-day
OL,10,Fclock pauses or stops" due to the
OL,11,Fceasefire.
OL,13,FMany Republicans had emphasised that
OL,14,Fthere would be a May 1 deadline for
OL,15,FCongress to intervene at the start of
OL,16,Fthe war, but no action has been
OL,17,Fplanned as the lawmakers take a one-
OL,18,Fweek break.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
