OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FA sixth bid to stop the war in Iran
OL,7,Fwas rejected in the Senate on
OL,8,FThursday, with two Republicans voting
OL,9,Fin favour of it.
OL,11,FIran vows to protect nuclear
OL,12,Fcapabilities
OL,14,FIt is not yet clear what Iran's latest
OL,15,Fpeace proposal entails, but Iran's
OL,16,Fsupreme leader vowed on Thursday to
OL,17,Fprotect the Islamic Republic's nuclear
OL,18,Fand missile capabilities, a major
OL,19,Fsticking point between the nations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
