OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FIn a statement read by a state
OL,7,Ftelevision anchor, Ayatollah Mojtaba
OL,8,FKhamenei said the only place the US
OL,9,Fbelonged in the Persian Gulf was "at
OL,10,Fthe bottom of its waters".
OL,12,F"Ninety million proud and honorable
OL,13,FIranians inside and outside the
OL,14,Fcountry regard all of Iran's identity-
OL,15,Fbased, spiritual, human, scientific,
OL,16,Findustrial and technological
OL,17,Fcapacities - from nanotechnology and
OL,18,Fbiotechnology to nuclear and missile
OL,19,Fcapabilities - as national," Khamenei
OL,20,Fsaid.
