OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FKhamenei has not been seen in public
OL,7,Fsince taking over as supreme leader
OL,8,Ffollowing the killing of his father in
OL,9,Fthe war's opening airstrikes.
OL,11,FKhamenei's aide, Mohsen Qomi, shut
OL,12,Fdown reports he is not well enough to
OL,13,Flead, stating that suggesting
OL,14,Fotherwise was "a trick by the enemy"
OL,15,Fon Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
