OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,F"Currently, he is in perfect health
OL,7,Fand is actively managing affairs. He
OL,8,Foversees matters related to
OL,9,Fnegotiations and field operations
OL,10,Funder his direct supervision," Qomi
OL,11,Ftold Fars News Agency, which is linked
OL,12,Fto the Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,13,FCorps.
OL,15,FIsrael-Lebanon strikes continue
OL,16,Fdespite ceasefire
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
