OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FThe Israel Defence Forces said on May
OL,7,F1 they had destroyed more than 40
OL,8,FHezbollah infrastructure sites in
OL,9,Fsouthern Lebanon in the last 24 hours,
OL,10,Fdespite a ceasefire between the
OL,11,Fcountries being extended last week.
OL,13,FResidents in the town of Habbouch, in
OL,14,Fsouthern Lebanon, were urged on Friday
OL,15,Fto evacuate their homes by at least
OL,16,F1,000 metres.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
