OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,F"In light of the terrorist Hezbollah
OL,7,Fparty violating the ceasefire
OL,8,Fagreement, the Defense Army is
OL,9,Fcompelled to act against it forcefully
OL,10,Fand does not intend to harm you,"
OL,11,FAvichay Adraee, the Arabic
OL,12,Fspokesperson for the IDF said on X.
OL,14,FSeventeen people, including two
OL,15,Fchildren, were killed in Israeli
OL,16,Fstrikes on southern Lebanon on
OL,17,FThursday, the country's health
OL,18,Fministry said, with a further 35
OL,19,Fpeople injured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
