OL,3,CTrump says he is 'not satisfied' with
OL,4,Clatest peace proposal from Iran
OL,6,FOne Israeli soldier was killed and
OL,7,Fthree others were injured in two drone
OL,8,Fattacks the same day.
OL,10,FHezbollah claimed the attack on
OL,11,FFriday, ITV News' US partner CNN
OL,12,Freports.
OL,14,FThe IDF said it had intercepted a
OL,15,Fdrone that was launched toward the
OL,16,Farea, and that a rocket and an
OL,17,Fexplosive drone launched by Hezbollah
OL,18,Fhad also fallen nearby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
